Mayoral, 23, has been growing into his role as understudy to Edin Dzeko, the Bosnian forward who is third on Roma's list of all-time top goalscorers.
Coach Paulo Fonseca has not ruled out the possibility of using the pair together, even if not immediately. 
"The team with this form is playing well. I don't need to change, but in the future it could be a possibility," he said.
Key stats
25 - Points between AC Milan and Torino
14 - Cristiano Ronaldo leads the Serie A goal-scoring charts
9 - League games Zlatan Ibrahimovic has missed
4 - Parma's losing streak
3 - Points between Inter and Roma
Fixtures (all times EAT)
